{
  "stem": "1858.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 342.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we ourselves-- you know, this was a slow degradation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we sort of like got used to looking the way we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a girl in our stube, in our room, who had epilepsy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And for 2 and 1/2 years, we managed to hide it from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But how sad that one month before the war had ended, she had a seizure during one of the cell appels and was removed, and we never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "How sad it was that only one month later, the war has ended.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, when they won, they gave us soap-- new soap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But not often we had soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the soap we called it the RIF.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It had the initials R-I-F, which they told us stood for Rein Judisches Fett, Pure Jewish Fat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know until today if that soap was actually made of human fat or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to give pain to the injury that we had already, they told us that it was made of Jewish fat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I say, I don't know if it was made or not, but telling us about it-- how we felt?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, we did not want to use that soap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, you know, the will to live persists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's the strongest of all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And wanting to live, wanting to keep clean, not because cleanliness was all that important to us, but there were all kinds of diseases raging throughout the camp, typhus, and all that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also a disease that settled between your fingers, [NON-ENGLISH], they called it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And wanting to be clean for the sake of living, we would scrape the initials and eventually began using the soap, having no other choice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, again, this added more pain to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
